<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Welcome to {{appName}}</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
        padding: 30px;
      }
      .container {
        background: #ffffff;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: auto;
        padding: 40px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      }
      h2 {
        color: #2d3748;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #4a5568;
      }
      .highlight-box {
        background: #f1f5f9;
        padding: 12px 20px;
        font-family: monospace;
        font-size: 16px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 15px 0;
        display: inline-block;
        color: #2d3748;
      }
      .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 20px;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #a0aec0;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Welcome to {{appName}}, {{userName}}</h2>

      <p>Youâ€™ve been added to <strong>{{appName}}</strong> as a <strong>{{userRole}}</strong>.</p>

      <p>Here are your login details:</p>
      <p><strong>Email:</strong> {{userEmail}}</p>
      <p><strong>Temporary Password:</strong></p>
      <div class="highlight-box">{{temporaryPassword}}</div>

      <p>
        Please log in using the button below and make sure to <strong>change your password</strong> immediately.
      </p>

      <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="cta-button">Log In to Your Account</a>

      <p>If you were not expecting this email, please contact us immediately.</p>

      <div class="footer">Need help? Contact support@{{appDomain}}</div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
